        {
            "title": "黑期跌225點  ADR低水142點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新加坡黑期報25484 點，跌225 點或0.88%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">根據高盛網站，港股ADR較恒指昨日收市低水142點或0.56%，報25573點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20230703-172008__source-web_HSBC-1_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20230703-172008__source-web_HSBC-1_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">外圍金融股跌，滙控(00005)倫敦股價跌3.5%，ADR則較港股收市低0.2%，折合港元計收報128.62元; 友邦保險(01299) ADR收市折合港幣83.26元，較香港收市價低1.3%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">阿里巴巴(09988) ADR較港收市價較港收市價低0.2%，報131.3元。騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣541.41元，較香港收市價低0.9% ; 美團 (03690)ADR收市折合港幣75.61元，較香港收市價低1.4% ;小米(01810) ADR收市折合港幣33.34元，較香港收市價0.1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指夜市期指收報25467點，跌233點，較昨日恒指收市25716點，低水250點，成交23996張。國指夜市期指收報8635點，較昨日國指收市低水65點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15736468-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e8%b7%8c225%e9%bb%9e-adr%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4142%e9%bb%9e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-3.jpg.webp",
